  <brief_title>2-D and 3-D Laparoscopic Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>3-dimensional Versus Conventional Laparoscopy in Patients Undergoing Total Hysterectomy for Benign Disease - A Randomised Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
