  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients referred for laparoscopic hysterectomy with or without bilateral
             salpingectomy or bilateral salpingooophorectomy for benign indications.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Women not suitable for laparoscopic hysterectomy including:

               -  Ultrasound appraisal of uterus weight &gt; 1000 gram

               -  Need for prolapse surgery and therefore indication for vaginal hysterectomy.

          -  Inability to give informed consent
      </textblock>
